om Imam Jafar Sadiq (a) that a person who recites YAA MUNTA-QIMO 661 times on every Eve of Friday (Shab’e Juma) for 3 Friday then his enemy will become weak and overpowered and will come and say sorry and will reconcile.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Hazrat Imam Ja’far Sadiq (a) se manqool hai keh jo shakhs YAA MUNTA-QIMO ko apna wazeefa (vird) bana kar har shab’e Juma 661 martaba vird kare aur is amal ko 3 shab’e Juma anjaam de, to us ka dushman maghloob o kamzor hoga hatta khud aa kar maazrat karega (maafi maangega) aur suleh karega.", "UrduDescription": "حضرت امام جعفر صادقؑ سے منقول ہے کہ جو شخص ’’یَا مُنْتَقِمُ‘‘ کو اپنا وظیفہ بنا کر ہر شب جمعہ 661 مرتبہ ورد کرے اور اس عمل کو 3 شب جمعہ انجام دے تو اس کا دشمن مغلوب و مقہور ہوگا حتٰی خود آکر معذرت کرے گا اور صلح کرے گا۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "Arab